item.title: Making a weapon way stonger than it should be
item.dc:creator: @Mendorphins Mendorphins
item.description:
@Mendorphins wrote:

Check to see where your item bonuses are loaded from, probably the item.cfg. Find the God swordâ€¦ and the second from last number is the strength bonus, edit that.

The last number is the prayer bonus and the first 3 are (in order) GENERAL STORE PRICE, LOW ALCH VALUE, HIGH ALCH VALUE.

The rest of the numbers are the attack and defence bonuses, respectively.
